parcel.name: B.20 Monument
parcel.description:
Welcome to B.20 - A $2.7 mn public art project from Metapurse. This estate is part of the B.20 bundle that comprises Beeple's iconic 1/1 everydays of 2020, housed in sprawling monuments crafted by Voxel Architects, on prime lands across the metaverse, and infused with original soundscape by 3LAU. The bundle is immutable and its ownership is fractionalized with B20 tokens. 
Open experience. Collective ownership.
